    <item>
      <title>Container Security</title>
      <link>https://mungops.github.io/devops/docker/docker03/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://mungops.github.io/devops/docker/docker03/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1&gt;컨테이너 격리 및 보안 🛡️&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2&gt;1️⃣ 네임스페이스와 cgroups 개념 🏗️&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-네임스페이스와-cgroups-개념-&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-%eb%84%a4%ec%9e%84%ec%8a%a4%ed%8e%98%ec%9d%b4%ec%8a%a4%ec%99%80-cgroups-%ea%b0%9c%eb%85%90-&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;1. 네임스페이스(Namespace)란?&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-네임스페이스namespace란&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-%eb%84%a4%ec%9e%84%ec%8a%a4%ed%8e%98%ec%9d%b4%ec%8a%a4namespace%eb%9e%80&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;📌 &lt;strong&gt;네임스페이스(Namespace)&lt;/strong&gt; 는 &lt;strong&gt;컨테이너 간의 격리를 제공&lt;/strong&gt;하는 Linux 커널 기능입니다.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;컨테이너가 서로 &lt;strong&gt;독립된 환경에서 실행&lt;/strong&gt;될 수 있도록 지원합니다.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Firecracker</title>
      <link>https://mungops.github.io/devops/docker/docker04/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://mungops.github.io/devops/docker/docker04/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1&gt;Firecracker 기반 경량 가상화 ⚡&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2&gt;1️⃣ Firecracker란? 🔥&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-firecracker란-&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-firecracker%eb%9e%80-&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;📌 &lt;strong&gt;Firecracker&lt;/strong&gt;는 AWS에서 개발한 &lt;strong&gt;경량 가상화(VMM, Virtual Machine Monitor)&lt;/strong&gt; 솔루션으로,&lt;br&gt;&#xA;서버리스 및 컨테이너 워크로드를 위한 &lt;strong&gt;초경량 가상 머신(MicroVM)&lt;/strong&gt; 실행을 지원합니다.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
